    "introduction": "Gala Hernández López is an artist-researcher and filmmaker. Her work accentuates interdisciplinary research with the production of essay films, video installations and performances, which explore new modes of subjectivation specifically produced by computational digital capitalism. She examines, through a feminist and critical lens, the discourses and imaginaries circulating in virtual communities as symptomatic fictions of the state of the world. Her work has been shown at DOK Leipzig, Cinéma du Réel, IndieLisboa, Transmediale and the Salon de Montrouge, among others.",
